Governor Emeka Ihedioha of Imo State says his administration will not relent in its avowed pursuit to meet the yearnings and expectations of the people. Ihedioha spoke during the swearing in of chairmen and members of Imo State House of Assembly Service, Imo State Civil Service, Imo State Law Reform and Local Government Service commissions at Sam Mbakwe Exco Chambers. Ihedioha suspends LG chairmen, councillors, appointees A likely scenario in Imo, come 2019 Breaking: APC missing as 67 vie for Imo governorship